 but I think Alan Lee was nominated at least once, and maybe twice, when the worldcon was in the United Kingdom.<br /><br />Your general point is right on, though: he is an AMAZING artist, and he should rightly have won a rocket or two by this point.","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 months ago","below":25691964,"ctime":"January 31 2017, 20:32:10 UTC","parent":25690940,"massactions":0,"subject":"","deleted":0,"username":[{"journal_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/","striked":null,"journaltype":"P","userhead_url":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net/img/userinfo_v8.svg?v=17080?v=146.10","color":null,"noctxpopup":0,"side_alias":0,"journal":"grrm","inline_css":0,"attrs":null,"is_identity":0,"bold":1,"show_userhead":1,"username":"grrm","user_alias":"","profile_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/profile","alias":0}],"dname":"grrm","ctime_ts":1485894730,"tracked":0},{"shown":1,"collapsed":0,"userpic":"http://l-userpic.livejournal.com/36918195/6781987","actions":[{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/519228.html?thread=25691708#t25691708","name":"permalink","title":"link"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/519228.html?thread=25691708#t25691708","name":"collapse","title":"Collapse"},{"allowed":1,"href":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/519228.html?thread=25691708#t25691708","name":"expand","title":"Expand"}],"uname":"f4f3","loaded":1,"p_tracked":0,"commenter_journal_base":"http://f4f3.livejournal.com/","statprefix":"http://l-stat.livejournal.net","dtalkid":25691708,"talkid":100358,"thread_url":"http://grrm.livejournal.com/519228.html?thread=25691708#t25691708","above":25691196,"upictitle":"f4f3: Strange","article":"I must confess, I only checked Wikipedia, who show the 5 short-listed nominees. Alan didn't make that short-list, but he's there lower down on the lists in several years that I can see. As you say, a fantastic artist (and a stand-up guy).","siteroot":"http://www.livejournal.com","poster":"grrm","stime":"3 months ag